<item>
            <title>[LU-3536] log updates for cross-MDT operation. </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3536</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For cross-MDT operation, the updates needs to be logged to all of MDT. So during recovery between MDTs, MDTs can read these update logs and check and redo the log. But this ticket is only for logging the update into the disk.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
